  "detailed_description": "<strong>Miasma</strong> is a first-person psychological horror maze game with a horrific atmosphere, it takes place in a maze with a mysterious creature lurking in it, and your only hope of survival is to find a way to escape.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447080/extras/7997f8537f90066c1a717f0b697d2995.avif?t=1772463076\" width=628 height=354 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SURVIVE</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447080/extras/b5735008aa7bda2d682b66823a6f56af.poster.avif?t=1772463076\" width=628 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447080/extras/b5735008aa7bda2d682b66823a6f56af.webm?t=1772463076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447080/extras/b5735008aa7bda2d682b66823a6f56af.mp4?t=1772463076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Investigate and survive this maze. But be careful, you are not alone.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tools</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447080/extras/bb527f88d07bb819a7fe062b099b9f48.poster.avif?t=1772463076\" width=628 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447080/extras/bb527f88d07bb819a7fe062b099b9f48.webm?t=1772463076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447080/extras/bb527f88d07bb819a7fe062b099b9f48.mp4?t=1772463076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use the motion tracker to locate the enemy but be careful. It can hear you<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HIDE OR FLIGHT</h2><br><span class